author: Luke Rosiak
description: The federal government awards research grants to universities to make scientific breakthroughs, but for every dollar that it is spent on science, up to 70 additional cents is diverted to administrators, a study found.
title: How Universities Divert Federal Science Grants To DEI And Administrative Bloat
